1. create a project
    django-admin startproject myproject
        a. settings.py
        b. urls.py

2. create an app
    cd myproject    -   manage.py

    python .\manage.py startapp helloworld
        __init__.py
        admin.py
        apps.py
        models.py
        tests.py
        views.py
        urls.py         -   create a new file